{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_YY03_120.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x13,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Fritz!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Sophie. What is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "To tell the truth, I want to ask about travel preparations..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Travel preparations...? Why would you ask that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Well, you see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hm, I see... So that's why..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "The list you wrote up is almost enough, but there's just one thing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh, really? What is it...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "A place to sleep. While traveling, securing places to sleep can be quite difficult."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I don't mind sleeping outdoors, but... That would be rather harsh for a young lady like yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat, that's not true. I'd be fine sleeping outside!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "...Oh really? You need unexpectedly good technique to sleep on the ground. You won't sleep well for a long time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Also, when you wake up, nearly every day you'll find yourself with insects, snakes, and more crawling on you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "And that's still the tame part. In the past, I've even experienced terrible..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I-I'm sorry! It really does sound like too much! I'm sorry for doubting you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Right? In that case, you need a secure place to sleep... Ah, I know. I think you should prepare a tent."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x52,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I see, a tent... I understand!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Yes. The most important part of traveling is to be fully prepared. Think it over carefully."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Okay!"
        }
    ]
}